name: Followup Table
query:
SELECT 
`tabFollow up`.date as "Date",
`tabLead`.company_name as "Organization",
`tabLead`.state as "State",
`tabLead`.city as "City",
`tabLead`.country as "Country",
`tabLead`.job_title as "Designation",
`tabLead`.mobile_no as "Mobile No",
`tabLead`.capacity as "Capacity",
`tabLead`.plant_type as "Plant Type",
`tabLead`.system_name as "System Name",
`tabLead`.future_expansion as "Future Expansion",
`tabLead`.enquiry_for as "Enquiry For",
`tabFollow up`.conversation as "Conversation",
`tabFollow up`.employee_name as "Employee Name",
`tabFollow up`.client_side_representative as "Client",
`tabFollow up`.result as "Result"
FROM `tabFollow up` INNER JOIN `tabLead` ON `tabLead`.name=`tabFollow up`.parent WHERE `tabFollow up`.wtt_representative=%(employee)s and `tabFollow up`.date>=%(from_date)s and `tabFollow up`.date<=%(to_date)s;
